{"tid":2153131,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"同宿印傭染疫 揭檢測漏洞  計劃不涵蓋非中介提供住處","createTime":"2020-08-12T10:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T11:00:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1aecd57953fd4261f7f750bab8549c1fde7238a0","tid":2153131,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:59:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/KVK7MI4PXMKBY5E2NEEOEIO7HE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FKVK7MI4PXMKBY5E2NEEOEIO7HE%2F&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7dqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=72e87a87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FKVK7MI4PXMKBY5E2NEEOEIO7HE%2F&h=d5464c52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/KVK7MI4PXMKBY5E2NEEOEIO7HE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n同宿印傭染疫 揭檢測漏洞 <br />\n計劃不涵蓋非中介提供住處<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8W6e2yLCdYv48h_L82NvtB3D7tU=/640x444/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PABFVDLFL53DJ4KQVSLD6TLBHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8W6e2yLCdYv48h_L82NvtB3D7tU%3D%2F640x444%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPABFVDLFL53DJ4KQVSLD6TLBHY.jpg&h=1317fb96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有五名外傭染疫的上環建安商業大廈，昨有人員消毒。<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港武漢肺炎疫情漸趨緩和，昨日新增33宗確診，是27日以來最低。不過，源頭不明的個案仍佔近半，包括再有印傭染疫，而且涉及兩個家庭，當中包括長者。涉事印傭履新前並非居於僱傭公司提供的宿舍，意味或不受政府外傭檢測計劃涵蓋，立法會議員認為屬漏洞，建議政府資助外傭轉工期間獨居酒店，減低染疫風險。<br />\n<br />\n昨日新增33宗確診個案中，有一宗是輸入個案，是一名38歲男海員，從印度經多哈抵港。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n近期確診個案數字回落，衞生署衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君認為政府及。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n昨日再多一名40歲印傭確診（第4159號個案），疫情至今累計有七名印傭染疫。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Fc72dfaiLl2Rzk7PTTB-8KflMek=/369x834/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NOJXCKNQZYUPEA4F7VHR3NXXU4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFc72dfaiLl2Rzk7PTTB-8KflMek%3D%2F369x834%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNOJXCKNQZYUPEA4F7VHR3NXXU4.gif&h=d878647a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n議員倡政府資助住酒店<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：再增四死 累計奪59命<br />\n<br />\n涉事印傭再於7月23至8月3日居於旺角一間宿舍，警方資料顯示位於長旺道長興大廈9樓，與約10名外傭同住。張竹君指該宿舍與僱。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n近日屢有外傭染疫，勞工處周日開始為所有入住職業介紹所住宿設施的外。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港僱傭代理協會主席張結民坦言，不少待業外傭並非居於中介宿舍，選。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員郭家麒同樣認為有關安排是防疫漏洞。他指外傭為弱勢。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，最早確診的印傭（第3664號個案）曾居住銅鑼灣希雲大廈，中心追。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"1a91f51f0704c1b2a9b366d3ba999525c6280a1c","tid":2153131,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"轉工俾酒店，港共邊有可能"}]}